---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const structuredData = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Person',
  name: 'Joshua Colmenar',
  url: 'https://knottyquant.com/about.html',
  sameAs: [
    'https://github.com/ItsKamatis',
    'https://linkedin.com/in/Colmenar',
  ],
  alumniOf: [
    { '@type': 'CollegeOrUniversity', name: 'Rutgers Business School' },
    { '@type': 'CollegeOrUniversity', name: 'Kean University' },
  ],
  knowsAbout: [
    'Quantitative finance',
    'Derivatives valuation',
    'Portfolio construction',
    'Risk measurement',
    'Numerical methods',
  ],
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About KnottyQuant and Joshua Colmenar's quantitative-finance research practice."
  canonicalPath="/about.html"
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <header class="page-hero page-shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>What's KnottyQuant?</h1>
    <p>A personal platform</p>
    <p>Projects, technical notes, and writing on derivatives, risk, portfolio construction, numerical methods, and topology.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="about-grid page-shell" aria-labelledby="site-principles-title">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">The site</p>
      <h2 id="site-principles-title">A cheeky name</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>Knotty, naughty, all wound up? Knotty, naughty, all wound up? They say great things come in three, so what gives? Maybe all those 3 things are true. Knot theory and its use in studying entangled structures such as protein knots. The connection to finance is broader topology, particularly topological data analysis. </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid page-shell" aria-labelledby="author-title">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Who's behind it</p>
      <h2 id="author-title">Joshua Colmenar</h2>
      <p>Quantitative-finance researcher focused on derivatives valuation, portfolio construction, risk measurement, and numerical implementation.</p>
    </div>
    <dl class="fact-list">
      <div>
        <dt>Education</dt>
        <dd>MS in Quantitative Finance, Rutgers Business School, 2026</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Undergraduate</dt>
        <dd>BS Finance and Economics, Kean University, 2024</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Tools</dt>
        <dd>Python, C++, pandas, NumPy, SciPy, CVXPY, PyTorch, SQL, and Excel</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Contact</dt>
        <dd><a href="mailto:anrucolmenar@gmail.com">Email</a> · <a href="https://github.com/ItsKamatis" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a> · <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/Colmenar" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
